title: DANSKDYNAMIT.COM font
content:

comments.content:
I don't think it's an existing/available font. Rather custom shapes/lettering. The logotype has been done by [Emil Kozak](http://web.archive.org/web/20150419134114/http:/emilkozak.com/category/work).
